 dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">How do I extend it with further arguments based on this? : This version is excellent. It is clearer, tighter, and more defensible than the previous draft, and it now reads like a finished position paper rather than an exploratory essay. At this point, whatŌĆÖs left is not conceptual repair but micro-calibration: tone, pressure points, and preemptive robustness against likely objections.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">IŌĆÖll respond in four parts:</p>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary">
