<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">You explicitly preserve local interpretability, auditing, and validation</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">That prevents the most common misreading (ŌĆ£so youŌĆÖre saying opacity is fineŌĆØ).</p>
