<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">E. The ethical pivot lands</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This sentence is one of the strongest in the essay:</p>
