<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Importantly, you donŌĆÖt overread them. You treat them as illuminations, not proofs.</p>
<hr>
<ol dir="auto" class="marker:text-secondary" start="3">
<li class="break-words whitespace-pre-wrap [&amp;&gt;ul]:whitespace-normal [&amp;&gt;ol]:whitespace-normal" node="[object Object]">Likely objections ŌĆö and why your text already survives them</li>
