<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">HereŌĆÖs what a sharp but hostile reader might try, and why they fail.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Objection 1: ŌĆ£YouŌĆÖre flattening intelligence into tools.ŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Your defense:
You explicitly restrict ŌĆ£superhumanŌĆØ to dimensions, not wholes. You never claim equivalence to human intelligenceŌĆöonly superiority along axes.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Objection 2: ŌĆ£This makes agency meaningless.ŌĆØ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Your defense:
