<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">The two frameworks overlap in striking ways, yet diverge sharply on several decisive axes. Both are resolutely anti-anthropocentric and treat non-humans as genuine actors, but they do so for almost opposite philosophical reasons and with very different normative consequences.</p>






































































