<h4 dir="auto" class="" node="[object Object]">1. Object-Oriented Ontology (Harman)</h4>



































<div class="relative"><div class="absolute top-1 right-1 z-10 print:hidden"><div class="flex flex-row gap-0.5"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium leading-[normal] cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:opacity-60 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-colors duration-100 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 select-none text-fg-secondary hover:text-fg-primary hover:bg-button-ghost-hover disabled:hover:text-fg-secondary disabled:hover:bg-transparent [&amp;_svg]:hover:text-fg-primary h-8 w-8 rounded-full dark:bg-surface-l1 dark:text-text-l1 dark:hover:bg-surface-l2" type="button" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><span style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-[2] size-4"><rect x="3" y="8" width="13" height="13" rx="4" stroke="currentColor"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M13 2.00004L12.8842 2.00002C12.0666 1.99982 11.5094 1.99968 11.0246 2.09611C9.92585 2.31466 8.95982 2.88816 8.25008 3.69274C7.90896 4.07944 7.62676 4.51983 7.41722 5.00004H9.76392C10.189 4.52493 10.7628 4.18736 11.4147 4.05768C11.6802 4.00488 12.0228 4.00004 13 4.00004H14.6C15.7366 4.00004 16.5289 4.00081 17.1458 4.05121C17.7509 4.10066 18.0986 4.19283 18.362 4.32702C18.9265 4.61464 19.3854 5.07358 19.673 5.63807C19.8072 5.90142 19.8994 6.24911 19.9488 6.85428C19.9992 7.47112 20 8.26343 20 9.40004V11C20 11.9773 19.9952 12.3199 19.9424 12.5853C19.8127 13.2373 19.4748 13.8114 19 14.2361V16.5829C20.4795 15.9374 21.5804 14.602 21.9039 12.9755C22.0004 12.4907 22.0002 11.9334 22 11.1158L22 11V9.40004V9.35725C22 8.27346 22 7.3993 21.9422 6.69141C21.8826 5.96256 21.7568 5.32238 21.455 4.73008C20.9757 3.78927 20.2108 3.02437 19.27 2.545C18.6777 2.24322 18.0375 2.1174 17.3086 2.05785C16.6007 2.00002 15.7266 2.00003 14.6428 2.00004L14.6 2.00004H13Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></span></button></div></div><div dir="auto" class="table-container relative group/table clear-both overflow-scroll flex flex-row" style="mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, black 85%, 92.5%, transparent 100%); mask-composite: add;"><div class="scroll-gradient-sentinel" style="height: 100%; width: 1px; left: 0px; flex-shrink: 0;"></div><table dir="auto" class="w-fit min-w-[calc(var(--content-width)-13px)] [&amp;&gt;thead&gt;tr&gt;th:last-child]:pr-8"><thead class="sticky [top:var(--thead-sticky-top)] [&amp;_th]:h-10 [background-color:var(--thead-bg-color)] [box-shadow:0_1px_0_0_var(--thead-border-b-color)] border-b-0" node="[object Object]"><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><th class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]">Dimension</th><th class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]">Graham HarmanŌĆÖs OOO</th><th class="break-words" data-col-size="xl" node="[object Object]">Abstraction/Agency Thesis</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Source of opacity</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Metaphysical surplus: real objects exceed every relation and every sensual profile</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="xl" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Engineered deficit degrees of freedom are deliberately discarded for scalability</td></tr><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Agency</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Ontological dignity + vicarious causation; every real object acts by surprising its neighbors</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="xl" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Persistent, generalizing, constraining internal structure; agency is not dignity but reliable effect propagation</td></tr><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Withdrawal</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Universal and eternal; even a hammer withdraws its molten essence from fire</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="xl" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Selective and engineered; humans are not withdrawn in the politically relevant sense (they retain meta-level suspension/refusal/defection)</td></tr><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Human exceptionalism</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Rejected; humans are one object among billions</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="xl" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Reintroduced negatively and precisely: humans remain the only entities capable of non-scalable refusal</td></tr><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Politics / safety</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Humility before inexhaustible depth; let objects surprise us</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="xl" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Governance through invariants + exogenous refusal mechanisms; interruptibility must be imposed from outside</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="scroll-gradient-sentinel" style="height: 100%; width: 1px; right: 0px; flex-shrink: 0;"></div></div></div>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Bottom line
OOO treats opacity as surplus depth ŌåÆ politics of wonder and respect.
The abstraction thesis treats opacity as engineered loss ŌåÆ politics of containment and enforced interruptibility.</p>
<h4 dir="auto" class="" node="[object Object]">2. Hyperobjects (Morton)</h4>








































<div class="relative"><div class="absolute top-1 right-1 z-10 print:hidden"><div class="flex flex-row gap-0.5"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium leading-[normal] cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:opacity-60 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-colors duration-100 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 select-none text-fg-secondary hover:text-fg-primary hover:bg-button-ghost-hover disabled:hover:text-fg-secondary disabled:hover:bg-transparent [&amp;_svg]:hover:text-fg-primary h-8 w-8 rounded-full dark:bg-surface-l1 dark:text-text-l1 dark:hover:bg-surface-l2" type="button" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><span style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-[2] size-4"><rect x="3" y="8" width="13" height="13" rx="4" stroke="currentColor"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M13 2.00004L12.8842 2.00002C12.0666 1.99982 11.5094 1.99968 11.0246 2.09611C9.92585 2.31466 8.95982 2.88816 8.25008 3.69274C7.90896 4.07944 7.62676 4.51983 7.41722 5.00004H9.76392C10.189 4.52493 10.7628 4.18736 11.4147 4.05768C11.6802 4.00488 12.0228 4.00004 13 4.00004H14.6C15.7366 4.00004 16.5289 4.00081 17.1458 4.05121C17.7509 4.10066 18.0986 4.19283 18.362 4.32702C18.9265 4.61464 19.3854 5.07358 19.673 5.63807C19.8072 5.90142 19.8994 6.24911 19.9488 6.85428C19.9992 7.47112 20 8.26343 20 9.40004V11C20 11.9773 19.9952 12.3199 19.9424 12.5853C19.8127 13.2373 19.4748 13.8114 19 14.2361V16.5829C20.4795 15.9374 21.5804 14.602 21.9039 12.9755C22.0004 12.4907 22.0002 11.9334 22 11.1158L22 11V9.40004V9.35725C22 8.27346 22 7.3993 21.9422 6.69141C21.8826 5.96256 21.7568 5.32238 21.455 4.73008C20.9757 3.78927 20.2108 3.02437 19.27 2.545C18.6777 2.24322 18.0375 2.1174 17.3086 2.05785C16.6007 2.00002 15.7266 2.00003 14.6428 2.00004L14.6 2.00004H13Z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></span></button></div></div><div dir="auto" class="table-container relative group/table clear-both overflow-scroll flex flex-row" style="mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, black 85%, 92.5%, transparent 100%); mask-composite: add;"><div class="scroll-gradient-sentinel" style="height: 100%; width: 1px; left: 0px; flex-shrink: 0;"></div><table dir="auto" class="w-fit min-w-[calc(var(--content-width)-13px)] [&amp;&gt;thead&gt;tr&gt;th:last-child]:pr-8"><thead class="sticky [top:var(--thead-sticky-top)] [&amp;_th]:h-10 [background-color:var(--thead-bg-color)] [box-shadow:0_1px_0_0_var(--thead-border-b-color)] border-b-0" node="[object Object]"><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><th class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]">Dimension</th><th class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]">Timothy MortonŌĆÖs Hyperobjects</th><th class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]">Abstraction/Agency Thesis</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Source of opacity</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Ontological-ecological scale + nonlocality; entities are too vast, viscous, and phased to be grasped</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Engineered reduction; opacity is the mathematical price of scalable compression</td></tr><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Distribution</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Viscous, nonlocal, temporally undulating, interobjective</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Persistent, generalizing, constraining; effects propagate through code, law, markets, infrastructure</td></tr><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Agency</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Overwhelmingly nonhuman; hyperobjects act on us more than we act on them</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Overwhelmingly non-intentional; abstractions act on us precisely because refusal was amputated</td></tr><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Refusal</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Overwhelms refusal by immersion (viscosity makes escape impossible</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Overwhelms refusal by amputationthe system was built without brakes</td></tr><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Political / ethical response</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Ecological attunement, lameness, caring from inside the mesh</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Structural containment + exogenous refusal (invariants, kill switches, institutional veto)</td></tr><tr class="border-primary/10" node="[object Object]"><td class="break-words" data-col-size="sm" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Overlap</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Some abstractions at planetary scale (e.g., the LLMŌĆōsociety complex) become hyperobject-like</td><td class="break-words" data-col-size="lg" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Acknowledged, but hyperobjects are a broader category not limited to engineered cognitive artifacts</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="scroll-gradient-sentinel" style="height: 100%; width: 1px; right: 0px; flex-shrink: 0;"></div></div></div>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" node="[object Object]" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Bottom line
Morton: we are inside the unmasterable ŌåÆ learn to lament and coexist.
Abstraction thesis: we built the unrefusable ŌåÆ enforce interruptibility and invariant bounds from outside.</p>
